
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
        }
        .order-details {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .order-details h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .order-details p {
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Order Confirmation By Learna</h1>
        <p>Course:- <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Your order has been successfully placed. Below are the details:</p>
        <div class="order-details">
            <h2>Order ID: <%= _id %></h2>
            <p>Price: <%= price %></p>
            <p>Date: <%= date %></p>
        </div>
        <p>Thank you for choosing Learna.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
